<li id="c43">
  <div class="cx" id="cx50280949">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">There are a lot of variables</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1211849/50280949#c43?mode=alone;showrate=1#c43">4+ / 0-</a>)</span>
