<p>If we do start investing in these trained educated individuals, our country will slowly decline. Corporate America must understand that it is the flow of money that makes our economy work. An if educated skilled workers can not get a job in their field of training and study, then what is the point of obtaining that education. We have to invest and innovate or stagnate and decline. By investing in people who will invest in their future. The flow of money through the economy.</p>

